description: Roll a dice using Alexa! This simple skill will give you a number between 1-6! Perfect for any game that involves using dice! Ask magic dice to roll and it will respond with a randomly generated number between 1 and 6.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask magic dice to roll
Alexa, ask magic dice to throw dice
Alexa, tell magic dice to give me a number
name: Magic Dice
shortDescription: Need to roll a dice? Well now Alexa can do it for you!
